Dialogue: 0.0:17:42.22.0:17:44.09.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(209.413)}What is going on. Rick?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:44.16.0:17:45.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(262.413)}I'm freaking out!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:45.79.0:17:47.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(243.371)}Calm down. Morty!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:45.79.0:17:47.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(164.413)}Look at me! Calm down. Morty!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:47.46.0:17:49.05.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(238.370)}No. I can't deal with
Dialogue: 0.0:17:47.46.0:17:49.05.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(335.410)}this!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:49.13.0:17:50.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(227.413)}Calm yourself. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:50.80.0:17:52.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(265.368)}I can't deal with
Dialogue: 0.0:17:50.80.0:17:52.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(298.412)}this. Rick!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:52.37.0:17:53.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(233.371)}- Calm down. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:52.37.0:17:53.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(240.410)}- This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:53.87.0:17:56.00.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(170.371)}- You gotta calm down. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:53.87.0:17:56.00.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(157.413)}- W-W-W-W-We're ripped apart!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:56.07.0:17:57.97.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(203.413)}Shut up and listen to me!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:58.04.0:17:59.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(314.368)}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:58.04.0:17:59.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(250.413)}Everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:59.37.0:18:00.84.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(195.368)}There's an infinite number
Dialogue: 0.0:17:59.37.0:18:00.84.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(248.413)}of realities. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:00.91.0:18:02.54.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(182.412)}and in a few dozen of those.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:02.61.0:18:04.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(226.371)}I got lucky and turned
Dialogue: 0.0:18:02.61.0:18:04.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(192.413)}everything back to normal.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:04.68.0:18:06.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(234.371)}I just had to find one
Dialogue: 0.0:18:04.68.0:18:06.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(257.410)}of those realities
Dialogue: 0.0:18:06.41.0:18:09.04.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(157.371)}in which we also happen to both
Dialogue: 0.0:18:06.41.0:18:09.04.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(232.410)}die around this time.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:09.12.0:18:10.61.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(233.371)}Now we can just slip
Dialogue: 0.0:18:09.12.0:18:10.61.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(277.413)}into the place
Dialogue: 0.0:18:10.69.0:18:12.18.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(244.368)}of our dead selves
Dialogue: 0.0:18:10.69.0:18:12.18.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(283.413)}in this reality
Dialogue: 0.0:18:12.25.0:18:13.88.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(192.413)}and everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:13.96.0:18:15.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(195.371)}We're not skipping a beat.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:13.96.0:18:15.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(324.413)}Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:15.42.0:18:16.45.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(206.371)}Now. help me with these
Dialogue: 0.0:18:15.42.0:18:16.45.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(317.410)}bodies.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:16.52.0:18:17.62.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(269.410)}This is insane.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:17.69.0:18:19.85.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(184.371)}Look. Morty. I'll grab myself.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:17.69.0:18:19.85.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(203.413)}you grab yourself. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:19.93.0:18:21.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(214.370)}I mean. t-t-t-that seems
Dialogue: 0.0:18:19.93.0:18:21.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(288.410)}fair to me --
Dialogue: 0.0:18:21.36.0:18:23.26.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(216.370)}I mean. that seems like
Dialogue: 0.0:18:21.36.0:18:23.26.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(212.413)}a fair way to divvy it up.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:23.33.0:18:25.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(257.370)}Rick. what about
Dialogue: 0.0:18:23.33.0:18:25.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(197.413)}the reality we left behind?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:25.43.0:18:28.10.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(177.371)}What about the reality where
Dialogue: 0.0:18:25.43.0:18:28.10.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(190.413)}Hitler cured cancer. Morty?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:28.17.0:18:29.64.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(236.368)}The answer is don't
Dialogue: 0.0:18:28.17.0:18:29.64.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(275.410)}think about it.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:29.70.0:18:31.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(200.368)}It's not like we can do this
Dialogue: 0.0:18:29.70.0:18:31.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(220.413)}every week. anyways.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:31.94.0:18:33.46.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(195.371)}We get three or four more
Dialogue: 0.0:18:31.94.0:18:33.46.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(271.413)}of these. tops.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:33.54.0:18:35.27.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(186.371)}Now. pick up your dead self
Dialogue: 0.0:18:33.54.0:18:35.27.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(274.410)}and come on.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:35.34.0:18:36.64.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(234.410)}Haste makes waste.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:36.71.0:18:38.84.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(204.371)}I-I-I don't suppose you've
Dialogue: 0.0:18:36.71.0:18:38.84.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(222.412)}considered this detail.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:38.91.0:18:41.41.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(213.371)}but obviously. if I hadn't
Dialogue: 0.0:18:38.91.0:18:41.41.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(175.413)}screwed up as much as I did.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:41.48.0:18:45.32.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(171.371)}we'd be these guys right now.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:41.48.0:18:45.32.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(192.413)}so. again. you're welcome.
