Dialogue: 0.0:19:05.37.0:19:11.18.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(261.368)}♪ Look on down
Dialogue: 0.0:19:05.37.0:19:11.18.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(252.413)}from the bridge ♪
