Dialogue: 0.0:19:43.01.0:19:49.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(256.368)}♪ It's no different
Dialogue: 0.0:19:43.01.0:19:49.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(181.413)}when you're leaving home ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:19:52.25.0:19:58.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(193.371)}♪ I can't be the same thing
Dialogue: 0.0:19:52.25.0:19:58.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(279.413)}to you now ♪
