Dialogue: 0.0:20:02.66.0:20:08.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(275.413)}♪ Just gone ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:20:08.37.0:20:15.37.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(169.413)}♪ How could I say goodbye? ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:20:16.38.0:20:20.54.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(169.413)}♪ How could I say goodbye? ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:20:20.68.0:20:24.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(234.371)}You know. the thing
Dialogue: 0.0:20:20.68.0:20:24.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(262.410)}about a shark...
Dialogue: 0.0:20:24.32.0:20:26.75.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(218.413)}he's got lifeless eyes...
Dialogue: 0.0:20:26.82.0:20:28.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(291.371)}black eyes.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:26.82.0:20:28.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(254.413)}like a doll's eyes.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:28.82.0:20:30.31.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(217.413)}When he comes at ya.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:30.39.0:20:32.33.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(185.371)}he doesn't seem to be living
Dialogue: 0.0:20:30.39.0:20:32.33.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(259.413)}until he bites ya.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:32.39.0:20:35.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(200.370)}and then the -- the blood.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:32.39.0:20:35.30.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(182.412)}and the red. and the water...
Dialogue: 0.0:20:35.36.0:20:36.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(313.413)}[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.0:20:36.43.0:20:38.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(149.371)}You ever wonder what happened
Dialogue: 0.0:20:36.43.0:20:38.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(241.413)}to Rick and Morty?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:38.67.0:20:41.43.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(287.368)}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:38.67.0:20:41.43.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(192.412)}But. I'm ashamed to admit.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:41.50.0:20:47.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(221.371)}now that they're gone.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:41.50.0:20:47.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(257.413)}I'm finally happy.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:47.14.0:20:49.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(281.370)}Here we are.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:47.14.0:20:49.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(233.413)}Cronenberg Morty --
Dialogue: 0.0:20:49.31.0:20:50.90.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(268.371)}a reality where
Dialogue: 0.0:20:49.31.0:20:50.90.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(224.413)}everyone in the world
Dialogue: 0.0:20:50.98.0:20:52.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(170.413)}got genetically Cronenberged.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:52.41.0:20:54.51.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(263.371)}We'll fit right in.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:52.41.0:20:54.51.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(243.413)}Cronenberg Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:54.58.0:20:57.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(203.368)}It'll be like we never even
Dialogue: 0.0:20:54.58.0:20:57.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(221.413)}left Cronenberg world.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:57.08.0:20:58.45.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(207.413)}Yeah. Cronenberg Rick.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:58.52.0:21:00.28.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(169.371)}but. you know. I'm gonna miss
Dialogue: 0.0:20:58.52.0:21:00.28.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(244.413)}Cronenberg world.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:00.35.0:21:02.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(245.371)}because everyone
Dialogue: 0.0:21:00.35.0:21:02.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(181.413)}was Cronenberged all along
Dialogue: 0.0:21:02.09.0:21:03.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(195.371)}like us from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:02.09.0:21:03.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(292.413)}you know?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:03.79.0:21:05.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(200.370)}I mean. I-I wish we hadn't
Dialogue: 0.0:21:03.79.0:21:05.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(250.413)}genetically ruined
Dialogue: 0.0:21:05.43.0:21:07.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(245.371)}Cronenberg World
Dialogue: 0.0:21:05.43.0:21:07.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(199.413)}beyond repair like we did.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:07.43.0:21:10.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(159.371)}you know. and turned everyone
Dialogue: 0.0:21:07.43.0:21:10.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(191.413)}into regular. normal people
Dialogue: 0.0:21:10.10.0:21:11.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(232.413)}just walking around.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:11.60.0:21:13.19.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(224.371)}Don't you worry about
Dialogue: 0.0:21:11.60.0:21:13.19.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(253.413)}that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:13.27.0:21:14.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(243.413)}Cronenberg Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:14.44.0:21:17.74.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(208.371)}Let's go make ourselves
Dialogue: 0.0:21:14.44.0:21:17.74.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(270.412)}at home. huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:21.44.0:21:22.88.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(212.413)}Did you get any of that?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:22.94.0:21:24.91.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(359.71)}It's a good-a show!
